A new commissioner of police, Philip Maku, has taken over at the Bauchi State Police Command. <img class="alignnone  wp-image-1291528" src="https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/NEW-CP.jpg?resize=640%2C759&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="640" height="759" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/NEW-CP.jpg?resize=253%2C300&amp;ssl=1 253w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/NEW-CP.jpg?resize=865%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 865w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/NEW-CP.jpg?resize=768%2C909&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/NEW-CP.jpg?resize=49%2C58&amp;ssl=1 49w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/NEW-CP.jpg?resize=164%2C194&amp;ssl=1 164w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/NEW-CP.jpg?resize=110%2C130&amp;ssl=1 110w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/NEW-CP.jpg?resize=560%2C663&amp;ssl=1 560w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/NEW-CP.jpg?w=912&amp;ssl=1 912w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Maku took over from Habu Sani who has been redeployed to Kano State. A statement issued on Tuesday by command’s Public Relations Officer, Kamal Datti, said the new police commissioner has assumed duty in the state. He said: “A new CP who is a seasoned police officer with vast experience in policing both within and outside Nigeria has assumed office in Bauchi. He is from Nasarawa Eggon local government area of Nasarawa State. Our new CP holds a bachelor’s degree in Business Administration from the prestigious Ahmadu Bello University, Zaria. He joined the Nigeria Police Force as Cadet Assistant Superintendent of Police in 1988. “Since then, he has occupied various positions both within and outside Nigeria. His last posting was Commissioner of Police in charge of Department of Logistics and Supply at Force Headquarters Abuja.”  Vanguard   The Bauchi Police Command has said that a new Commissioner of Police has been posted to Bauchi State to take over from the outgoing Police Commissioner, Ali Janga. May 6, 2019 In "News" The Bauchi Police Command has said that a new Commissioner of Police has been posted to Bauchi State to take over from the outgoing Police Commissioner, Sanusi Lemu. January 8, 2019 In "News" The Nigeria Police Force, Bauchi State Command said it has launched a new strategy it called "Sectoral Community Policing" to improve security in the State. May 25, 2019 In "News"